---
title: Teriyaki Ginger Beef Bowl with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Make a simple stir-fry a little more special by serving with mouth-watering garlic rice! Plus, using our delicious teriyaki sauce means you get a big helping of flavour with minimal effort. Enjoy your tasty and colourful creation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-ginger-beef-bowl-e9b493f8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/teriyaki-ginger-beef-bowl-5fe0158bdbcb0f583f017b1a-bbdb2727.pdf
